description:
I, as a skilled guild member, was tasked with breaking the Duke of Verwinte's wedding.

'This marriage is invalid! I... have the Duke's child.'

My unexpected confession made quite a stir in the wedding reception hall.

'It seems like the wedding will be ruined, so should I just leave?'

Just as I was about to leave the wedding hall, Veriwinter approached me and said,

'Honey, why are you so late?'

'Ho- honey? Did you just call me honey?'

“I almost got married for real.”

'…?!'

'Leaving our child behind.'

…Excuse me but I have never seen you before!>
